<plot>Two down-and-out Hollywood screenwriters living together ('Arye Gross'(qv) and 'Tom Wood (II)'(qv)) in a self-storage facility suspect that the man who rents space next to them (Ron Perlman'(qv)) is the infamous Costume Killer--a serial murderer who stalks the streets of Los Angeles decked out in ridiculous rented outfits. Using their neighbor's misdeeds for inspiration, the two friends desperately try to write a hit screenplay... at any cost.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?608976</url></doc>
